{
  "page": "Gage",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Gage</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Turnip\" title=\"Turnip\">Turnip</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gage</b> is the head cook at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He has a child, <a href=\"/index.php/Turnip\" title=\"Turnip\">Turnip</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Gage eagerly awaits the return of game hunters to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> When there are lemons to be had, he makes <a href=\"/index.php/Lemon_cake\" title=\"Lemon cake\">lemon cakes</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Gage also bakes beef-and-bacon pies<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and steak-and-kidney pies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a> is upset, and his <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Shaggydog\" title=\"Shaggydog\">Shaggydog</a> bites Gage's arm.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> The captured <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> is sent to work with Gage in the kitchen. The cook has a sexual relationship with Osha, who finds Gage gentler than her former lover, <a href=\"/index.php/Stiv\" title=\"Stiv\">Stiv</a>. Gage lets Osha pray in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Godswood of Winterfell\">godswood of Winterfell</a> from time to time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Osha helps Gage with cooking, baking, and cleaning in the kitchens.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> The cook is sullen toward <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> after the <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">capture of Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Theon Greyjoy and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a> escape Winterfell, and are discovered by <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Umber\" title=\"Mors Umber\">Mors Umber</a>. Crowfood asks Jeyne questions about the castle to confirm her assumed identity of \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\", such as the names of servants, including <a href=\"/index.php/Mikken\" title=\"Mikken\">the smith</a> and the cook. Jeyne immediately answers with Gage's name, and Mors assumes the cook died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Well, your <a href=\"/index.php/Dream\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dream\">dreams</a> are your business. Mine's in the kitchens, and I'd best be getting back before Gage starts to shouting and waving that big wooden spoon of his.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Osha\" title=\"Osha\">Osha</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Mors</b>: When last I was inside those walls, your cook served us a steak and kidney pie. Made with <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a>, I think, best I ever tasted. What was his name, that cook?<br />\n<b>Jeyne</b>: Gage. He was a good cook. He would make <a href=\"/index.php/Lemon_cake\" title=\"Lemon cake\">lemoncakes</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> whenever we had lemons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Umber\" title=\"Mors Umber\">Mors Umber</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 4\">Chapter 4</a>, Bran I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_51\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 51\">Chapter 51</a>, Jon VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-TWOW-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-TWOW_4-3\">4.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Theon I (The Winds of Winter)\">Theon I</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, Jon IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_53\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 53\">Chapter 53</a>, Bran VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, Bran VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_66\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 66\">Chapter 66</a>, Theon VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403181000\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.087 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.262 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1224/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11207/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9678/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1778/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5001/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.32 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  245.361      1 -total\n 88.93%  218.198      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 87.91%  215.699      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.66%   26.163     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.62%   18.703     10 Template:Ref\n  4.58%   11.229     10 Template:Ref/core\n  4.38%   10.747      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.46%    3.571      1 Template:References\n  0.92%    2.258      2 Template:Quote\n  0.81%    1.988      1 Template:Warning/twow\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3082-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403180959 and revision id 321989\n -->\n",
